result:
Due to current situation of COVID-2019, the committee of RCAR 2020 has determined to change the conference to be a virtual one. The committee is now requiring authors to submit a presentation video for use in the coming online conference in the case when no authors of the paper can make a real-time presentation. The details on how to prepare for and upload the presentation video can be found in final submission page in the conference site. The registration site and the schedule of the online conference will be announced soon.

Program committee of RCAR 2020

Aug. 25, 2020
